{"tid":386972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲孝順仔嫌買錯飲品　木棍打到父母跳落街","createTime":"2017-09-04T09:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T14:53:20.000Z","uid":126293,"like":8,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a319db0b410d77783ee7310baae248a7aa38de9","tid":386972,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:52:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170904/mobile/bkn-20170904015252662-0904_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170904%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170904015252662-0904_00822_001.html&d=2O%2FuI0XC9AMasLbiUOLmrE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3c41e5f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170904/mobile/bkn-20170904015252662-0904_00822_001.html</a><br />\n沙田發生孝順仔棍打父母事件。消息指，昨晚11時許，博泉街水泉澳邨嶺泉樓一名83歲姓楊老而不，替其17歲孝順仔買飯，回到家卻被發現飲品冷熱出錯，兒子與其老父及姓黃(54歲)的母親發生激烈口交。期間，孝順仔情緒激動，喝罵兩老而不，更出手以老父的木棍枴杖毆打兩老而不，兩老而不分別頭及手受傷，負傷逃出屋外，並到樓下大堂向當值保安求助，由保安代為報案。 <br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，以涉嫌襲擊致造成身體實際傷害將兩老拘捕，案件交由沙田警區刑事調查隊跟進。傷者孝順仔由救護車送院治理。"},{"pid":"757199c0f2284364792b4c6a2d80409c7d7ed5e0","tid":386972,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dea8b48f4f8339001ecf2484b5223ee57f1c29f","tid":386972,"uid":2022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb52fa6f4205ebfd1317ea752f48e0868552d421","tid":386972,"uid":58145,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"孝順仔棍打父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7363774c675cf8bc5c793ac4ce5ebe8ba2a6dc03","tid":386972,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f93470095847c28ab22aa73cdb17eb7b7343c8a","tid":386972,"uid"